calculated_columns.name: Daily cases
calculated_columns.expression:
VAR __CountyName = 'COVID'[County Name]
VAR __State = 'COVID'[State]
VAR __Yesterday =  DATEADD(COVID[Date],-1,DAY)
VAR __TodaysCases = 'COVID'[Cases]

RETURN  __TodaysCases - CALCULATE(
    SUM('COVID'[Cases]) , 
    FILTER(
        COVID, 
        COVID[Date] = __Yesterday &&
        COVID[County Name] = __CountyName &&
        COVID[State] = __State
    )
) + 0
calculated_columns.expression_formatted:
VAR __CountyName = 'COVID'[County Name]
VAR __State = 'COVID'[State]
VAR __Yesterday = DATEADD(COVID[Date], -1, DAY)
VAR __TodaysCases = 'COVID'[Cases]
RETURN __TodaysCases - CALCULATE(SUM('COVID'[Cases]),
    FILTER(COVID, COVID[Date] = __Yesterday && COVID[County Name] = __CountyName && COVID[State] = __State))+ 0
